<?xml version="1.0" encoding="Windows-1252"?>
<!--Info:
    Supported Gesture Types: 
    * Physical 
    * Voice
    For a full list of available XBMC Commands, see : http://wiki.xbmc.org/?title=Action_IDs
    Steps to Add a new Gesture:
    1. Implement the Gesture Segments in The Fizbin.Gestures.Segments namespace of this project.
    2. Implement the ICompositeGesture interface to combine the segments and add an ID to your gseture.
    3. In this file, add a new entry with you gesture name and type and any XBMC ActionId in the Command field.
    4. That's it! The new gesture will automatically be loaded and registerd in Runtime.
-->
